t":"不如说，正是因为做过调查@我才得出了这个结论…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":103701,"motion":0,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103005/vo_full_103005-10-12"}],"nameRight":"那由他","textRight":"正是因为做过调查…？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":802401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103005/vo_full_103005-10-13"}],"nameLeft":"太助","textLeft":"魔法少女的存在总是很难扩散，@已经到了不自然的程度"},{"chara":[{"id":802401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103005/vo_full_103005-10-14"}],"nameLeft":"太助","textLeft":"你还记得这个结论吗？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103701,"motion":1,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103005/vo_full_103005-10-15"}],"nameRight":"那由他","textRight":"是的"},{"chara":[{"id":103701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103005/vo_full_103005-10-16"}],"nameRight":"那由他","textRight":"比如说，谁都不会对有关@魔法少女的事件和事故感到违和"},{"chara":[{"id":103701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103005/vo_full_103005-10-17"}],"nameRight":"那由他","textRight":"又比如，一般来说@都会对魔法少女的事保密…"},{"chara":[{"id":103701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103005/vo_full_103005-10-18"}],"nameRight":"那由他","textRight":"这些在访问过神滨市和二木市@这些地方之后感受到的事情…"},{"chara":[{"id":802401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103005/vo_full_103005-10-19"}],"nameLeft":"太助","textLeft":"嗯，是的"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bgm":"stop","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter9/103005_old_puella_magi.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm21_system01","nameNarration":"太助","narration":"「在调查过过去的历史之后@我对周围的人不会感到违和@这件事的疑问进一步膨胀了」","narrationCoverOpacity":150,"narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103005/vo_full_103005-10-20"},{"narration":"「正如从那由他那里听说的丘比的说法@就算说是魔法少女也不会不可思议的人们@却只会被作为神话、英雄谭和传说口口相传下来」","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103005/vo_full_103005-10-21"},{"narration":"「不过，不管怎样解构些内容@并从中发现足以认为是魔法少女的记述@她们的事迹也只会被作为个人的特例描绘」","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103005/vo_full_103005-10-22"},{"narration":"「不管是在阿